window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I told him my deepest, darkest secret. And in turn, he made my wish come true.</b></p> <p>She's the shy girl. The one you'd never notice.</p> <p>But I did. I watched her, studied her. While she worked in the library, meticulously rearranging books as though she'd written them herself.</p> <p>I wanted her, so I made her an offer she couldn't refuse. Tell me your deepest, darkest wish... And I will make it come true.</p> <p>One whisper...</p> <p>One single wish...</p> <p>And I bought her soul.</p> <p>Dark Wish <i>is an enticing new dark romance by </i>New York Times <i>and</i> USA Today <i>bestselling author Clarissa Wild. For mature listeners.</i></p> <p><i>Narrated in duet style.</i></p>"; 
